Gotta Take The Time Out To Thank All The Fans And Supporters. 

 I Really Appreciate You! 
When Starting Out On This Journey With The Name Change And Building My Own Brand And Independent Company, I Didn’t Know What To Expect Or How You Would Perceive My Growth As A Man, An Executive & Artist. 
 I Wanna Say I’m Truly Humbled And Appreciative For The  Support. 
From The Bottom Of My Heart I Wanna Thank You For Embracing The
 (Highly Favored E.P) And Making It The Staple And Foundation Of Our Mission. 
I Promise Next Year We Will Drop More Consistent Music & Content, As Well As Introduce A New Artist Or 2 Under The TEA Imprint. 

Stay Tuned! 
“Highly Favored 2” Coming Soon 1st Quarter Of 2024, And I Can’t Wait For Y’all To Check It Out!
